<id>p037v_5</id>
<ab>
41. It would be good if you acquaint yourself first<lb/>
with your story, from Scriptures or Poets as you please,<lb/>
to link your Landscape to it better.<lb/>
But above all, and never forget,<lb/>
to add Small Figures to large Trees.<lb/>
The little World you have made is ready to enter,<lb/>
there to mow, over there, to travel by wagon,<lb/>
elsewhere to fish, sail, fly and hunt.<lb/>
</ab>

<ab><margin>left-middle</margin>That it is good to know one’s History already.</ab>
<ab><margin>left-middle</margin>Small Figures next to large Trees.</ab>
