42. Here let Peasant Maidens loosen their hands<lb/>
from the Milk-springs along the verdant shore,<lb/>
there <i>Tityrus</i> with his Flute brings delight<lb/>
to Amaryllis, his most beloved of Women,<lb/>
sitting in repose under the Beech tree;<lb/>
and beguiles his herd with sweet sounds.<lb/>
Yes, fill your Country, City, and Water with activity;<lb/>
populate your Houses; place wanderers on your roads.<lb/>
